'''西藏行动中心'''（{{lang-en|Tibet Action Institute}}）是一个使用数字通信工具与战略性非暴力行动来增强数字时代的西藏运动的能力和效力的组织，<ref name="democracy2019">{{cite web|url=https://www.ned.org/defenders-of-human-and-religious-rights-in-china-to-receive-2019-democracy-award-on-30th-anniversary-of-tiananmen-massacre/|title=DEFENDERS OF HUMAN AND RELIGIOUS RIGHTS IN CHINA TO RECEIVE 2019 DEMOCRACY AWARD ON 30TH ANNIVERSARY OF TIANANMEN MASSACRE|date=21 May 2019|accessdate=6 May 2020|website=National Endowment for Democracy|archive-date=2019-05-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190527113201/https://www.ned.org/defenders-of-human-and-religious-rights-in-china-to-receive-2019-democracy-award-on-30th-anniversary-of-tiananmen-massacre/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>该组织帮助识别、追踪和抵抗针对藏族活动分子发起的恶意软件和其他类型的在线攻击。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://editors.cis-india.org/raw/civil-society-organisations-and-internet-governance-in-asia-open-review|title=Civil Society Organisations and Internet Governance in Asia - Open Review|date=19 August 2015|accessdate=6 May 2020|website=[[Centre_for_Internet_and_Society_(India)|Centre for Internet and Society (India)]]|author=Sumandro Chattapadhyay|archive-date=2020-11-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201126004926/http://editors.cis-india.org/raw/civil-society-organisations-and-internet-governance-in-asia-open-review|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 历史 ==
[[File:Students_for_a_Free_Tibet_Honors_Beijing_Olympics_Activists_at_Victory_Party_in_New_York_自由西藏-圖博學生運動在紐約慶功宴嘉許參與北京奧運行動人士.jpg|thumb]]于2009年2月19日在纽约市的胜利晚会向北京奥运会的活动家致敬，特别嘉宾[[班旦加措|班旦加措]]身穿长袍站在最中心。|alt=]]

2012年，西藏行动中心主任志彤•拉珍解释西藏的自焚事件，是对中国政府不断加剧的镇压的回应。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/world/asia_pacific/china-powerless-to-prevent-rising-tide-of-tibetan-self-immolations/2012/10/30/e3149830-22ac-11e2-8448-81b1ce7d6978_story.html|title=China powerless to prevent rising tide of Tibetan self-immolations|date=30 October 2012|accessdate=6 May 2020|website=[[Washington_Post|Washington Post]]|author=Simon Denyer|archive-date=2020-12-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201209051950/https://www.washingtonpost.com/world/asia_pacific/china-powerless-to-prevent-rising-tide-of-tibetan-self-immolations/2012/10/30/e3149830-22ac-11e2-8448-81b1ce7d6978_story.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2013年，公民实验室（Citizen Lab）的工作人员与西藏行动中心合作，在印度[[达兰萨拉|达兰萨拉]]举办了针对流亡西藏社区网络间谍活动的公众讲座。<ref>{{cite web|title=Tibet Action Institute: Safe Travels Online Tech Meet|date=June 12, 2013|url=https://cyberstewards.org/2013/06/public-awareness-program-on-internet-security-and-a-talk-on-targeted-threats-against-the-tibetan-community/|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140325174023/https://cyberstewards.org/2013/06/public-awareness-program-on-internet-security-and-a-talk-on-targeted-threats-against-the-tibetan-community/|archivedate=2014-03-25|via=[[Internet_Archive|Internet Archive]]|access-date=2020-08-22|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2018年3月，西藏行动中心放映了一部纪录片“以孔子之名”（In the Name of Confucius），批评波士顿的[[孔子学院|孔子学院]]]。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.theepochtimes.com/perspectives-on-the-pandemic-why-the-ccp-virus-spread-in-massachusetts_3330973.html|title=CCP Virus Outbreak in Massachusetts Illustrates Ties With Chinese Regime|date=5 May 2020|accessdate=6 May 2020|website=[[Epoch_Times|Epoch Times]]|author=Liu Jingye|quote=In March of that year, the Tibet Action Institute hosted a screening of “In the Name of Confucius” in Boston.|archive-date=2021-02-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210216012600/https://www.theepochtimes.com/perspectives-on-the-pandemic-why-the-ccp-virus-spread-in-massachusetts_3330973.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2019年，西藏行动中心获得[[美国国家民主基金会|美国国家民主基金会]]颁发的“民主奖”。<ref name="democracy2019"/>

